body.content:
Attention My Dearest,

Sir,

Greetings to the Lord.  I'm Dr. James Fernau , a lawyer in Cotonou, Benin
Republic. Late Mr. David Jorge, a gold merchant who was my client, died as
a result of lung cancer without a will, now I want to present your name to
late Mr. David Jorge, bank so that money left behind by late Mr. David
Jorge, can be transferred into your account through my help.

The amount of US$ 18.5 million deposited in a local bank here, by late Mr.
David Jorge before his death on November 23, 2012, I need your information
so that I can show you the bank as next of kin to Late Mr. David Jorge for
further process. Harm and risk free and sure everything legal to achieve
this goal.

Please provide name and full address, your age, profession and position,
address and mobile number for contact purposes.

Thank you kindly.
Yours Faithfully.
Dr. James Fernau
